KR:
&lt;메피스토펠레스로 바로 연결되는 거였구나…&gt;
EN:
&lt;So this passageway leads straight into Mephistopheles...?&gt;

KR:
&lt;응?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Hm?&gt;

KR:
&lt;…!&gt;
EN:
&lt;…!&gt;

KR:
&lt;알고 있었어?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Did you know that this would work?&gt;

KR:
&lt;…파우스트, 그러면 우리가 원래 받았던 의뢰는…&gt;
EN:
&lt;... Faust, what about the job we were contracted to do in the first place...?&gt;

KR:
&lt;…….&gt;
EN:
&lt;…….&gt;

KR:
&lt;그럼… 이 열차의 승객… 그리고 앞으로 탈 승객들은?&gt;
EN:
&lt;But... what about the other passengers of this train? And its future passengers?&gt;

KR:
&lt;포기해야… 하는 거야?&gt;
EN:
&lt;... Are we going to have to let them... die?&gt;

KR:
&lt;도, 돈키호테…&gt;
EN:
&lt;D-Don Quixote...&gt;

KR:
&lt;돈키호테… 열쇠가 사라지면 다른 수감자들이 몇천 년을 고통받게 될 거야.&gt;
EN:
&lt;Don Quixote... Letting him destroy that key means that you'll be condemning the Sinners to thousands of years of torment.&gt;

KR:
&lt;자, 잠깐만! 돈키호테, 피해!&gt;
EN:
&lt;W-wait! Don Quixote, NO!&gt;

KR:
&lt;…!&gt;
EN:
&lt;…!&gt;

KR:
&lt;파우스트…? 해결이라니…?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Faust...? What do you mean... 'the solution'...?&gt;

KR:
&lt;돈키호테, 왜 그렇게 평소에 그 운동화를 애지중지 하는 거야?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Why are you always so... protective of those running shoes, Don Quixote?&gt;

KR:
&lt;응… 그거…&gt;
EN:
&lt;Uh... yeah, those.&gt;

KR:
&lt;아냐, 됐어…&gt;
EN:
&lt;Nope, I think I'm good...&gt;

KR:
&lt;돈키호테, 설마 그 운동… 아니, 로시난테를 신고 잠도 자는 거야?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Don Quixote, don't tell me you go to sleep wearing those running sh— I mean, Rocinante.&gt;

KR:
&lt;로시난테를 벗은 적은 있어?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Have you ever taken them... off?&gt;

KR:
&lt;으으윽…!&gt;
EN:
&lt;Gnnngh…!&gt;

